<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-79-0946 </DOCNO><TEXT>A photovoltaic (PV) system is an economical solution for power supplyproblems of telecommunication stations in rural areas. Photovoltaicsis a new concept and consequently the standards and specifications havenot yet been fully developed. This paper presents some aspects aboutspecifying, sizing, and designing a PV-system. Also some experienceson carrying out a large telecommunication project with PV-systems inNepal are represented.</TEXT></DOC>